  "english": [
    "<b>Rabbi Yosei said:</b> Now <b>they will say: Meir is dead, Yehuda is angry,</b> and <b>Yosei remained silent</b> and did not respond. If so, <b>what will become of the Torah? Rabbi Yosei</b> therefore <b>said:</b> It is <b>not necessary</b> to teach that a nazirite must shave for impurity imparted by a corpse, <b>but</b> only that he must shave even <b>for</b> impurity imparted by <b>a corpse upon which there is not an olive-bulk of flesh.</b> The Gemara asks: <b>But one could still say:</b> If he must <b>shave for</b> impurity imparted by <b>a limb from</b> a corpse, even if it is less than an olive-bulk, as stated in the mishna, is it <b>not all the more so</b> that he must shave <b>for</b> impurity imparted by <b>all of</b> a corpse, even if it does not contain an olive-bulk of flesh?",
    "<b>Rather,</b> the mishna should be explained <b>as Rabbi Yoḥanan said,</b> with regard to a different issue: It is <b>necessary only for a miscarried fetus whose limbs had not</b> yet <b>become joined to</b> its <b>sinews. Here too,</b> one can say that the mishna’s statement that a nazirite must shave for impurity imparted by a corpse is referring <b>to a miscarried fetus whose limbs had not</b> yet <b>become joined to</b> its <b>sinews.</b> Although it does not impart impurity through one of its limbs, as the limbs lack sinews and bones, this corpse itself does impart impurity.",
    "<b>Rava said</b> a different explanation: This ruling is <b>necessary only for the majority of the structure or the majority of the number</b> of bones of a very small corpse, despite the fact <b>that</b> together <b>they do not contain a quarter-</b><i>kav</i> <b>of bones.</b> Since these bones comprise the majority of the structure or the majority of the number of bones of a corpse, they have the status of a whole body. This <i>halakha</i> could not have been derived from the measure of impurity of part of the body, as this corpse is very small.",
    "§ The mishna taught: A nazirite shaves <b>for</b> impurity imparted by <b>an olive-bulk of a corpse and for</b> impurity imparted by <b>an olive-bulk of fluid.</b> The Gemara explains: <b>And what is fluid?</b> This is referring to <b>flesh of the corpse that</b> liquefied and subsequently <b>congealed, and liquid [<i>mohal</i>]</b> from the corpse <b>that</b> began <b>to boil</b> and then hardened.",
    "The Gemara asks: <b>What are the circumstances</b> in which the congealment is a determinative factor in the imparting of impurity? <b>If we say that we do not know that</b> the substance with which the nazirite came into contact <b>is</b> from the corpse, even <b>if</b> it <b>congealed, what of it? Rather,</b> you will say <b>that we know that it</b> came from the corpse. But then the nazirite should be impure <b>even though</b> it has <b>not congealed.</b>",
    "<b>Rabbi Yirmeya said</b> that this is referring <b>to an unspecified</b> substance that is definitely from the corpse but is not necessarily a substance that imparts impurity. One therefore examines the substance: <b>If</b> the substance eventually <b>congeals, it is liquid</b> from the corpse, which imparts impurity; if it does <b>not congeal, perhaps it is his phlegm and his spittle,</b> which do not impart impurity.",
    "§ With regard to the impurity of fluids from a corpse, <b>Abaye raised a dilemma before Rabba: Is there</b> the category of <b>fluid with regard to animals, or is there no</b> category of <b>fluid with regard to animals?</b> In other words, does fluid from an animal carcass impart impurity like the animal carcass itself or not? The Gemara explains the two sides of the dilemma: <b>Do we say</b> that it <b>is learned</b> as a tradition that <b>fluid that comes from a person</b> is impure <b>but</b> fluid <b>that comes from an animal</b> is <b>not</b> impure? <b>Or perhaps</b> it <b>is no different,</b> as fluid from a corpse is always considered like the flesh itself?",
    "The Gemara comments: <b>This works out well according to the one who says</b> that a carcass imparts impurity by <b>a severe impurity,</b> through contact and carrying, only <b>until</b> the carcass becomes inedible <b>for a stranger,</b> i.e., in order impart impurity it must be fit for human consumption. <b>And</b> the carcass imparts impurity by <b>a light impurity</b> that imparts impurity on food through contact <b>until</b> the carcass become inedible <b>for a dog.</b> According to this opinion, <b>it is well,</b> as the <i>halakha</i> of fluid certainly does not apply to an animal, since meat that has liquefied is no longer fit for human consumption.",
    "<b>However, according to the one who says</b> that a carcass imparts impurity by <b>a severe impurity until</b> it becomes inedible <b>for a dog, what is there to say?</b> Since fluids from an animal carcass are presumably fit to be eaten by a dog, the above dilemma as to whether it is impure remains pertinent.",
    "The Gemara answers: <b>Come</b> and <b>hear</b> a resolution from the <i>Tosefta</i> (<i>Zavim</i> 5:9): The fat of an animal carcass <b>that</b> someone <b>liquefied in fire is</b> still <b>impure.</b> However, if it melted <b>in the sun,</b> which impairs its taste, it is <b>pure. And if it enters your mind</b> that according to the opinion that a carcass imparts impurity <b>until</b> it becomes inedible <b>for a dog</b> the impurity of fluids does apply to an animal carcass, if so, <b>even</b> fat that dissolved <b>in the sun</b> should <b>also</b> be impure. Even if its taste is spoiled, it remains edible for a dog.",
    "The Gemara answers: <b>When does</b> this fat <b>liquefy? After it has putrefied,</b> which is why it was thrown out, at which point it melted <b>in the sun.</b> However, <b>once it putrefied, it had</b> already <b>become</b> like <b>dust</b> and lost any status of ritual impurity it once had. Once it has melted, it is no longer edible for a dog. Consequently, this source provides no proof.",
    "§ The Gemara discusses a related issue. <b>We learned</b> in a mishna (<i>Makhshirin</i> 5:9): <b>Anything that is poured</b> remains <b>ritually pure.</b> In other words, if one pours liquid from one vessel into another, the stream of liquid is not considered to connect the two vessels. Consequently, if the upper vessel and its contents are pure, they do not become impure even if the lower vessel into which the liquid is poured is impure. The stream of liquid does not link them in this manner.",
    "The mishna adds: This is the case for all liquids <b>except for <i>zifim</i> honey,</b> a very thick type of honey, <b>and batter,</b> e.g., flour mixed with honey. Since these substances are highly viscous, they are not considered liquids. Rather, they are a kind of soft solid food, which means that they are a single unit that links the two vessels with regard to impurity."
  ],
  "gemara": [
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"0\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר רַבִּי יוֹסֵי: יֹאמְרוּ מֵאִיר שָׁכַב, יְהוּדָה כָּעַס,",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "יוֹסֵי שָׁתַק — תּוֹרָה מַה תְּהֵא עָלֶיהָ? אָמַר רַבִּי יוֹסֵי: לֹא",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נִצְרְכָה אֶלָּא לְמֵת שֶׁאֵין עָלָיו כְּזַיִת בָּשָׂר.",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "וַעֲדַיִין יֹאמַר: עַל אֵבֶר מִמֶּנּוּ מְגַלֵּחַ, עַל כּוּלּוֹ",
      "segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "לֹא כׇּל שֶׁכֵּן?! <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"1\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֶלָּא, כִּדְאָמַר רַבִּי יוֹחָנָן: לֹא",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נִצְרְכָה אֶלָּא לְנֵפֶל שֶׁלֹּא נִתְקַשְּׁרוּ אֵבָרָיו",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּגִידִין. הָכָא נָמֵי: בְּנֵפֶל שֶׁלֹּא נִתְקַשְּׁרוּ אֵבָרָיו",
      "segment_ids": [
        1
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּגִידִין. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"2\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>רָבָא אָמַר: לֹא נִצְרְכָה אֶלָּא לְרוֹב",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בִּנְיָינוֹ וּלְרוֹב מִנְיָינוֹ, שֶׁאֵין בָּהֶן רוֹבַע עֲצָמוֹת.",
      "segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"3\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>עַל כְּזַיִת מֵת וְעַל כְּזַיִת נֶצֶל. וְאֵיזֶהוּ נֶצֶל —",
      "segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "בְּשַׂר הַמֵּת שֶׁקָּרַשׁ, וּמוֹהַל שֶׁהִרְתִּיחַ. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"4\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>הֵיכִי",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דָּמֵי? אִילֵּימָא דְּלָא יָדְעִינַן דְּדִידֵיהּ הוּא, כִּי קָרַשׁ",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מַאי הָוֵי? אֶלָּא דְּיָדְעִינַן דְּדִידֵיהּ הוּא, אַף עַל גַּב",
      "segment_ids": [
        4
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דְּלֹא קָרַשׁ! <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"5\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אָמַר רַבִּי יִרְמְיָה: בִּסְתָם. אִי קָרַשׁ —",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "מוֹהֵל הוּא, לֹא קָרַשׁ — דִּלְמָא כִּיחוֹ וְנִיעוֹ הוּא.",
      "segment_ids": [
        5
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"6\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>בְּעָא מִינֵּיהּ אַבָּיֵי מֵרַבָּה: יֵשׁ נֶצֶל לִבְהֵמָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אוֹ אֵין נֶצֶל לִבְהֵמָה? מִי אָמְרִינַן גְּמִירִי",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נֶצֶל דְּאָתֵי מֵאָדָם, אֲבָל דְּאָתֵי מִבְּהֵמָה — לָא. אוֹ",
      "segment_ids": [
        6
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "דִלְמָא לָא שְׁנָא? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"7\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>הָנִיחָא לְמַאן דְּאָמַר טוּמְאָה",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "חֲמוּרָה עַד לְגֵר, וְטוּמְאָה קַלָּה עַד לְכֶלֶב — שַׁפִּיר.",
      "segment_ids": [
        7
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "<span class=\"sentence\" id=\"8\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֶלָּא לְמַאן דְּאָמַר טוּמְאָה חֲמוּרָה עַד לְכֶלֶב, מַאי",
      "segment_ids": [
        8
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "אִיכָּא לְמֵימַר? <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"9\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תָּא שְׁמַע: הִמְחוּהוּ בָּאוּר — טָמֵא, בַּחַמָּה —",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "טָהוֹר. וְאִי סָלְקָא דַעְתָּךְ עַד לְכֶלֶב, אֲפִילּוּ בַּחַמָּה",
      "segment_ids": [
        9
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "נָמֵי! <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"10\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>אֵימַת מַמְחֵי לֵיהּ — בָּתַר דְּאַסְרַח בְּחַמָּה,",
      "segment_ids": [
        10
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "כֵּיוָן דְּאַסְרַח — הָוֵה לֵיהּ עָפָר. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"11\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>תְּנַן: כׇּל הַנִּצּוֹק —",
      "segment_ids": [
        11
      ]
    },
    {
      "right": "275px",
      "width": "380px",
      "text": "טָהוֹר. <span class=\"sentence\" id=\"12\" type=\"start\">&star;</span>חוּץ מִדְּבַשׁ הַזִּיפִים וְהַצַּפִּיחִית.",
      "segment_ids": [
        12
      ]
    }
  ],
  "rashi": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>וַעֲדַיִין יֹאמַר: עַל אֵבֶר מִמֶּנּוּ מְגַלֵּחַ.</b> ובלבד שיהא עליו בשר כראוי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ואע\"פ שאין עליו כזית בשר על מת כולו לא כ\"ש: <b>כי</b> <b>אמר</b> <b>ר\"מ</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>דעל</b> <b>מת</b> <b>מגלח</b> <b>כי</b> <b>ההיא</b> <b>דאמר</b> <b>ר'</b> <b>יוחנן</b> <b>לא</b> <b>נצרכה</b> <b>אלא</b> <b>לנפל</b> <b>כו'.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ובמס' חולין קאי וה\"נ בנפל שלא נתקשרו אבריו בגידין יפה יפה אמר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ר\"מ דמיטמא ואע\"פ שאין עליו בשר:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:1:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        0
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>רָבָא אָמַר.</b> כי אמר ר\"מ ברוב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בניינו של מת או ברוב מניינו שאין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עליהן כזית בשר ואין בין כולו רובע",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הקב עצמות דאע\"ג דבעלמא לא הוי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חשיב לענין טומאת אהל אא\"כ שיהא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בהן רובע עצמות גבי נזיר הוי חשוב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כמת שלם הואיל דאית ביה רוב בניינו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "או רוב מניינו שהוא מיטמא עליו ומגלח",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "עליהם: <b>שקרש.</b> שנימוח ואח\"כ קרש:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>וּמוֹהַל שֶׁהִרְתִּיחַ.</b> שיצא מבשר המת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כמין מים והרתיח ליקרש ע\"י רתיחות",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שהרתיח דכל הני נצל כבשר המת דמי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ונזיר מגלח עליו: <b>נצל.</b> לשון הפרש כמו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ויצל אלהים (בראשית לא): <b>היכי</b> <b>דמי</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>אילימא</b> <b>דלא</b> <b>ידעינן.</b> אי ההיא משקה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דקרש הוי מן המת כלומר דידעינן ודאי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דלאו ממת הוא: <b>כי</b> <b>קרש</b> <b>אמאי</b> <b>מיטמא.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הא ידעי' דלאו ממת הוא: <b>ואי</b> <b>מן</b> <b>המת</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>הוא.</b> בודאי אפילו לא קרש אמאי לא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מטמא: <b>א\"ר</b> <b>ירמיה</b> <b>בסתם.</b> כלומר",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ספוקי מספקא לן אי דמת הוי אי לא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הלכך אי קרש ודאי מגופיה של מת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הוא ולא כיחו וניעו ואי לא קרש דלמא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כיחו וניעו הוא דהא ליכא כיחו וניעו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "במת טמא דכל המשקים היוצאים ממת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "טהורין חוץ מן הדם: <b>כי</b> <b>גמירי.</b> דנצל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מטמא ההוא דאתי מאדם אבל נצל",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דאתי מבהמה לא מטמא כנבלה: <b>או</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>דלמא</b> <b>לא</b> <b>שנא</b> <b>והניחא.</b> דלא איצטריך",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ליה למיבעי אית ליה נצל או לא אליבא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "דמ\"ד דטומאה חמורה כלומר דטומאת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נבלה הוי לעולם כל זמן דחזי לאכילה לגר הלכך כיון דנצל הוא לא",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "חזי לאכילת אדם לא מטמא: <b>אלא</b> <b>למ\"ד</b> <b>דטומאה</b> <b>חמורה</b> <b>לעולם</b> <b>הוא</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>עד</b> <b>דמיפסל</b> <b>מאכילת</b> <b>כלב</b> <b>הכא</b> <b>מאי.</b> מי אמרי' כיון דאכתי חזי לאכילת",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כלב אכתי מטמא כזית נבלה או דלמא כיון דנמוח כעפרא בעלמא דמי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "ולא מטמא טומאה קלה: <b>עד</b> <b>לכלב.</b> כל זמן שלא תיפסל מאכילת כלב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שאינה מוסרחת כ\"כ שהכלב אינו רוצה לאוכלה: <b>ת\"ש.</b> חלב נבלה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "שהמחהו באור שהתיכו באור: <b>טמא.</b> דעדיין אוכל ראוי הוא: <b>המחהו</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "<b>בחמה</b> <b>טהור.</b> דפרחה טומאתו: <b>ואי</b> <b>ס\"ד</b> <b>דיש</b> <b>נצל</b> <b>לבהמה</b> <b>אפי'</b> <b>המחהו.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "בחמה ליהוי טמא כי חזר וקרש: <b>לעולם</b> <b>אימא</b> <b>לך</b> <b>דיש</b> <b>נצל</b> <b>לבהמה.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "והכא היינו טעמא דכי המחהו בחמה טהור דאימת קא ממחי ליה חמה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "לבתר דאסרח וכיון דאסרח תו לא חזי אפי' לאכילת כלב ומשום הכי",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "טהור ואינו מטמא אפי' בטומאה קלה: <b>תנן</b> <b>התם</b> <b>כל</b> <b>הניצוק</b> <b>טהור.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כל משקין שמריקין מכלי אל כלי אע\"פ שנטמא תחתון וקילוח יורד",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משפה לשפה לא נעשה חיבור כדי לטמא העליון: <b>חוץ</b> <b>מדבש</b> <b>הזיפים.</b>",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "מאותו דבש שהוא עבה ויכולין לזייפו לערב בו משקין אחרים וזיפים",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "משמע לשון זיוף כדמפ' במס' סוטה בפ' בתרא (<a href=\"/sotah/48b\">דף מח:</a>): <b>והצפיחית.</b> כמו",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "כצפיחית בדבש (<a href=\"https://www.sefaria.org/Exodus.16.31\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" data-sefaria-ref=\"Exodus.16.31\">שמות ט״ז:ל״א</a>) ברישקרי\"ש בלע\"ז והואיל והן עבין נעשה",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "תחתון כמו מחובר לעליון שהקילוח היורד למטה למשקין טמאין",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "נעשה כולו טמא ואפילו העליון אבל דבש שלנו שאינו עב",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "0px",
      "left": "",
      "text": "הואיל וצלול הוא ניצוק שבו טהור ככל המשקין:",
      "source_ref": "Rashi on Nazir 50a:4:2",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        3
      ]
    }
  ],
  "tosafot": [
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "<big><b>רָבָא אָמַר.</b></big>",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "390px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "והיינו על המת דקתני במתני' דליכא אבר",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "שלם ולרבותא נקט שאין בהם רובע עצמות דשיעורא דנזיר הוא בחצי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "450px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "קב (אלא לרבותא) דאע\"פ שאין בו רובע עצמות הוא מגלח כיון שיש",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "בו רוב הבנין או רוב המנין אבל אם",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אין בו רוב הבנין או רוב המנין אינו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מגלח אא\"כ יש בו חצי קב כדאמרינן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "במתני' דאין מגלח על אהל רובע עצמות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ואית ספרים דגרסי לא נצרכה אלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לשדרה וגולגולת שאין בו רובע עצמות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "והכי נמי בפרקין לקמן (דף נג. ושם)",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "פריך והאמר רבא לא נצרכה אלא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "לשדרה וגולגולת שאין בו רובע עצמות",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ולא מצינו שאמר רבא בעלמא אם לא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "כאן ולכך הגיהו בספרים כן ולא גרסי'",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "ליה דהיכי מצינן למימר דעל המת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דמתני' איירי בשדרה וגולגולת והא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "קתני במתני' בהדיא ועל השדרה ועל",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "הגולגולת לכך יש לגרוס [אלא] לרוב בנינו ולרוב",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מנינו (ליקוטי גרסאות) דלא תניא במתני' בפירוש ומהאי",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "טעמא נמי ניחא אמאי לא משני רבא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "אמתני' דאהלות כדמשני הכא על המת",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "דקתני התם לרוב בנינו או לרוב מנינו",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "משום דבמתני' דבאהלות קתני בהדיא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "על רוב בנין או על רוב מנין דמטמא",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "באהל הלכך ליכא לפרושי התם על",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "המת אלא כר' יוחנן וא\"כ לר' יוחנן",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "תנא ושייר במתני' רוב בנינו ורוב",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
      ]
    },
    {
      "width": "250px",
      "right": "",
      "left": "0px",
      "text": "מנינו אי ס\"ל דנזיר מגלח עלייהו.",
      "source_ref": "Tosafot on Nazir 50a:3:1",
      "gemara_segment_ids": [
        2
